        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4106563634" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5129462038473893624"><i>American Rust</i><br/><br/>Leaves other books in the dust.<br/><br/>I could go on at length about its big themes, its forays into stream of consciousness, its acute peeling back of the disintegration of the rustbelt economy and what unfettered capitalism looks like, its compelling portrait of crabbed lives and blighted families, until every aspect was discussed<br/><br/>But instead I’ll just say that <i>American Rust</i><br/><br/>Is a must.</span>

