          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/6667452-american-rust">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6787827-linda?shelf=2016">2016</a>
